        <script type="text/javascript">
         function showEmbed() {
    generateEmbed();
    //pb.toggleClass('#embedarea', 'is-visible');
    $('#embedarea').slideToggle(100, function() {
        var flashVideo = $("#myFlashMovie74049")[0];
        if (flashVideo) {
            flashVideo.forceShowAll($('#embedarea').is(':visible'));
        }
    });
    $('#vEmbedButton').toggleClass('target-visible');
    this.blur();
}

function selectAll(id) {
    document.getElementById(id).focus();
    document.getElementById(id).select();
}

function changeEmbedWidth() {
    var embedWidth = document.getElementById("embed_width").value;
    embedHeight = Math.round(embedWidth / 1.7391304347826);
    document.getElementById("embed_height").value = embedHeight;
    generateEmbed();
}

function changeEmbedHeight() {
    var embedHeight = document.getElementById("embed_height").value;
    embedWidth = Math.round(embedHeight * 1.7391304347826);
    document.getElementById("embed_width").value = embedWidth;
    generateEmbed();
}

function generateEmbed() {
    var embedWidth = document.getElementById("embed_width").value;
    var embedHeight = document.getElementById("embed_height").value;
    var color1 = document.getElementById("embed_color1").value;
    color1 = color1.substr(1);
        var colors = "?colors=";
    colors = colors + color1;
        var autoplay = "";
    if ($("#embed_autoplay").is(':checked')) {
        autoplay = "&amp;a=1"
    }
    var loop = "";
    if ($("#embed_loop").is(':checked')) {
        loop = "&amp;loop=1"
    }
    var showheadshot = "";
    if (!$("#embed_showheadshot").is(':checked')) {
        showheadshot = "&amp;showheadshot=0"
    }
    var showtitle = "";
    if (!$("#embed_showtitle").is(':checked')) {
        showtitle = "&amp;showtitle=0"
    }
    var showbyline = "";
    if (!$("#embed_showbyline").is(':checked')) {
        showbyline = "&amp;showbyline=0"
    }
    var showplaybutton = "";
    if (!$("#embed_showplaybutton").is(':checked')) {
        //showplaybutton = "&amp;showplaybutton=0"
    }
    var showcontrols = "";
    if (!$("#embed_showcontrols").is(':checked')) {
        //showcontrols = "&amp;showcontrols=0"
    }
    document.getElementById("embedCode").value = "&lt;iframe width='" + embedWidth + "' height='" + embedHeight + "' src='http://www.pinkbike.com/v/embed/74049/" + colors + autoplay + loop + showheadshot + showtitle + showbyline + showplaybutton + showcontrols + "' allowfullscreen frameborder='0'&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;";
        
}

function changeColor1() {
    var color = document.getElementById("embed_color1").value;
    color = color.substr(1);
    $("#myFlashMovie74049")[0].changeColor(0, color);
    generateEmbed();
}

$(document).ready(function() {
    $('#embedarea input:checkbox').click(function() {
        if ($(this).attr("id") == "embed_showheadshot") {
            $("#myFlashMovie74049")[0].showHeadshot($(this).is(':checked'));
        } else if ($(this).attr("id") == "embed_showtitle") {
            $("#myFlashMovie74049")[0].showTitle($(this).is(':checked'));
        } else if ($(this).attr("id") == "embed_showbyline") {
            $("#myFlashMovie74049")[0].showByLine($(this).is(':checked'));
        } else if ($(this).attr("id") == "embed_showplaybutton") {
            $("#myFlashMovie74049")[0].showPlayButton($(this).is(':checked'));
        } else if ($(this).attr("id") == "embed_showcontrols") {
            $("#myFlashMovie74049")[0].showControls($(this).is(':checked'));
        }
        generateEmbed();
    });
    
    $("#embed_color1").spectrum({
        showInput: true
    });
});
        </script>
